   "(define-values (ffi-doc-structured-ast-string-alist) (quote ((\"ffi-standard\" . \"(doc (meta (format \\\"ffi-structured-markdown\\\") (version 1) (slug \\\"ffi-standard\\\") (title \\\"standard.ffi Reference\\\") (source \\\"DOCS-standard.md\\\") (output \\\"documentation-ffi-standard.html\\\")) (h1 (code \\\"standard.ffi\\\") \\\" Reference\\\") (h2 \\\"Chapter 1 — Introduction\\\") (p \\\"This document describes the JavaScript FFI exported by \\\" (code \\\"ffi/standard.ffi\\\") \\\" in WebRacket.\\\") (p \\\"What this API gives you:\\\") (ul (li \\\"Access to JavaScript globals (\\\" (code \\\"Math\\\") \\\", \\\" (code \\\"Date\\\") \\\", \\\" (code \\\"Intl\\\") \\\", typed arrays, etc.).\\\") (li \\\"Property reads/writes and method calls on external JS objects.\\\") (li \\\"Controlled conversion between JS values and WebRacket values.\\\") (li \\\"Number helpers that mirror JavaScript \\\" (code \\\"Number\\\") \\\" static/instance behavior.\\\")) (p \\\"All functions below include:\\\") (ul (li \\\"input/output types\\\") (li \\\"a concrete example call\\\") (li \\\"a short “use when” note\\\") (li \\\"a link on the function name to the corresponding MDN documentation page\\\")) (p \\\"Assumption in examples: the program is compiled with \\\" (code \\\"--ffi ffi/standard.ffi\\\") \\\".\\\") (h3 \\\"Table of Contents\\\") (ul (li (link \\\"Chapter 1 — Introduction\\\" \\\"#chapter-1--introduction\\\")) (li (link \\\"Type Legend\\\" \\\"#type-legend\\\")) (li (link \\\"Conversion Rules\\\" \\\"#conversion-rules\\\")) (li (link \\\"Chapter 2 — Core Interop Functions\\\" \\\"#chapter-2--core-interop-functions\\\")) (li (link \\\"2.1 Value Properties\\\" \\\"#21-value-properties\\\")) (li (link \\\"2.2 Value Predicates\\\" \\\"#22-value-predicates\\\")) (li (link \\\"2.3 Global Function Properties\\\" \\\"#23-global-function-properties\\\")) (li (link \\\"2.4 Variables, Properties, and Indexing\\\" \\\"#24-variables-properties-and-indexing\\\")) (li (link \\